---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Join ICN" description="Get started with the InterCooperative Network.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="bg-accent-primary/20 text-accent-primary border border-accent-primary/30 text-sm font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-4 inline-block">
          GET STARTED
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Join the InterCooperative Network</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-light-slate max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          ICN is ready for pilot deployment. Whether you're a developer, a cooperative,
          or a community, here's how to get involved.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8">
        <!-- For Developers -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-primary mb-6">For Developers</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            ICN is open source and built in Rust. Clone the repo, run the tests, and start exploring.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg p-4 font-mono text-sm text-light-slate mb-6">
            <pre>git clone https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn
cd icn
cargo build --release
cargo test</pre>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-primary text-midnight-navy font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-primary/90 transition-colors">
              View Source Code
            </a>
            <a href="/docs"
               class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-transparent border-2 border-accent-primary text-accent-primary font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-primary hover:text-midnight-navy transition-colors">
              Read the Docs
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- For Cooperatives -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-blue/20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-blue mb-6">For Cooperatives</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            ICN provides infrastructure for timebanks, mutual credit systems, and cooperative
            coordination. The Pilot Web UI is ready for community deployment.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-light-slate space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-blue">✓</span>
              <span>Member identity management with DIDs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-blue">✓</span>
              <span>Mutual credit ledger for time banking and exchange</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-blue">✓</span>
              <span>Democratic governance with proposals and voting</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent-blue">✓</span>
              <span>Full mobile support with CSV export for treasurers</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/get-started"
             class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-blue text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-blue/90 transition-colors">
            Deployment Guide
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- For Communities -->
        <div class="bg-midnight-navy/50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-purple/20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-purple mb-6">For Communities</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6">
            Join our community to learn, discuss, and contribute to the cooperative internet.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <a href="https://discord.gg/GCWKPWdvgH"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-purple transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">Discord</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">Real-time chat and community discussions</p>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/InterCooperative-Network/icn/discussions"
               target="_blank"
               rel="noopener noreferrer"
               class="block p-4 bg-midnight-navy rounded-lg border border-slate-600 hover:border-accent-purple transition-colors">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">GitHub Discussions</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-gray text-sm">Proposals, Q&A, and longer-form collaboration</p>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Next Steps -->
        <div class="bg-accent-glow/10 p-8 rounded-lg border border-accent-glow/30 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent-glow mb-4">Next: Track C1 - Pilot Deployment</h2>
          <p class="text-light-slate mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            ICN is PILOT-READY with 20 development phases complete and 1,134+ tests passing.
            We're seeking cooperative communities for real-world pilot deployments.
          </p>
          <a href="mailto:hello@intercooperative.network"
             class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-accent-glow text-midnight-navy font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-accent-glow/90 transition-colors">
            Contact Us About Pilots
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
